      "description": "**Phase 1 & 2 Feature Highlights:**\n- **Vault Badges & Customization**: Set custom colors and icons for each vault via settings. They display beautifully next to search results.\n- **Advanced Filtering**: Use the new dropdown in Command Center to filter searches to a specific vault.\n- **Sorting Options**: Sort your results by Relevance, Newest, Oldest, or Vault Name.\n- **Include Patterns**: Limit a vault's indexing scope to specific folders.\n- **Cache Management**: Added a Clear Cache button and internal versioning to prevent future conflicts.",
